data.description: Welcome to your dream home! With its beautiful landscaping, backyard, four bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, stainless steel appliances, open concept design, this home truly offers the perfect blend of comfort, craftsmanship, and utility. The main living area features large windows that let in an abundance of natural light, making the space feel warm and inviting. The large kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a high bar counter. You will find the formal dining room at the front of the house. The house has four spacious bedrooms, each thoughtfully designed with cathedral ceilings. The primary suite is particularly impressive, allowing for plenty of natural light. The ensuite features a walk-in shower, seating area and elegant fixtures. Finally, check out the garage ready for all your toys and tools!
